    "Implementation DetailsThe implementation of Mistral LLM, augmented with the Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) technique, marks a pivotal step in enhancing the model's capacity for conducting comprehensive literature reviews.",
    "The fine-tuning of Mistral LLM with a bespoke corpus designed to mimic the literature review process preludes the integration of the RAG component.",
    "This strategic enhancement enables the model to dynamically retrieve and synthesize relevant information throughout the review process.",
    "The procedural integration of Mistral LLM with RAG for automatic literature review is outlined in Algorithm 1, ensuring the production of reviews that are not only contextually coherent but also imbued with the analytical depth characteristic of scholarly work.",
    "The fine-tuning and RAG integration were executed within a high-performance computing framework to efficiently manage the dataset's processing demands."
